A color cell|Washington Huskies}};\"|<small>6</small> '''[[2018 Washington Huskies football team|<span style=\"color:white;\">Washington Huskies</span>]]''' || 16\n| 70,103\n|-\n|[[2019 NCAA Division I FBS football season|2019]]\n| August 31, 2019\n| style=\"{{NCAA color cell|Alabama Crimson Tide}};\"|<small>2</small> '''[[2019 Alabama Crimson Tide football team|<span style=\"color:white;\">Alabama Crimson Tide</span>]]''' || '''42'''\n| style=\"{{NCAA color cell|Duke Blue Devils}};\"|'''[[2019 Duke Blue Devils football team|<span style=\"color:white;\">Duke Blue Devils</span>]]'''||3\n| 71,916<ref>{{cite web |title=Duke vs. Alabama - Game Summary - August 31, 2019 |url=https://www.espn.com/college-football/game/_/gameId/401110720 |website=ESPN.com |accessdate=1 September 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n<small>Rankings are from the [[AP Poll]].</small>\n\n== Future games ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Season\n!Date\n! colspan=\"2\" |Matchup\n!Source\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2020\n|September 5, 2020\n| style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Florida State Seminoles|border=0}}|<small></small> '''[[Florida State Seminoles football|{{color|#FFFFFF|Florida State Seminoles}}]]'''\n| style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|West Virginia Mountaineers|border=0}}|<small></small> '''[[West Virginia Mountaineers football|{{color|#FFFFFF|West Virginia Mountaineers}}]]'''\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/17153841/florida-state-seminoles-west-virginia-mountaineers-close-finalizing-2020-game-atlanta|title=Sources: FSU, WVU close to finalizing 2020 game in Atlanta|last=McMurphy|first=Brett|date=July 27, 2016|website=[[ESPN]]|url-status=live|access-date=July 27, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|September 7, 2020\n| style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Georgia Bulldogs|border=0}}|<small></small> '''[[Georgia Bulldogs football|{{color|#FFFFFF|Georgia Bulldogs}}]]'''\n| style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0}}|<small></small> '''[[Virginia Cavaliers football|{{color|#FFFFFF|Virginia Cavaliers}}]